'''Beldir''' (born {{FA|316}}) was a [[Men|man]] of the [[House of Bëor]].
== History ==
Beldir was the son of [[Belen]]. He had one son himself, [[Belemir]], who was born in {{FA|339}}.<ref name=WJBeor/>

